/hpc2hdd/home/xhao390/py/urbanclip/data/: The image captures a panoramic view of a street in Beijing, China. The perspective is from a high angle, providing a bird's eye view of the scene. The street is lined with trees and buildings, creating a harmonious blend of nature and architecture. Cars and bicycles are parked along the sides of the street, adding a touch of everyday life to the scene. Overhead, power lines crisscross the sky, a common sight in many urban areas. The colors in the image are predominantly green and gray, reflecting the natural and man-made elements of the scene.
